  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b9f \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 -\u00a0\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Special arrangement to bring vegetables from Nuwara Eliya to Colombo - Nuwara Eliya District Secretary",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nuwara Eliya District Secretary Nandana Kalapada stated that a special operation has been launched to transport vegetables from the Nuwara Eliya District to Colombo from today (01) Friday.",
        "He said that due to the shortage of fuel in the country, a new operation was being carried out to supply fuel through the army to transport essential items from Nuwara Eliya to Colombo.",
        "Despite many problems in transporting vegetables to Colombo, the Department of Agriculture, the Ministry of Agriculture and the Army should be thanked for taking this initiative.",
        "Meanwhile, he further mentioned that there is only one week of fuel for this essential requirement."
      ],
